OL,3,CBoy, 15, died trying to save friend in
OL,4,Ctragic quarry accident
OL,6,FA teenage boy who fell from a quarry
OL,7,Fdied after trying to save his friend
OL,8,Ffrom falling, an inquest has heard.
OL,10,FMyron Davies, 15, was pronounced dead
OL,11,Fat the scene after the incident at
OL,12,FAbersychan quarry, near Pontypool, on
OL,13,FJuly 6, 2022.
OL,15,FDuring the same incident, a 14-year-
OL,16,Fold girl also fell from the quarry and
OL,17,Fwas airlifted to the University
OL,18,FHospital of Wales, Cardiff, in a
OL,19,Fcritical condition.
