OL,3,CBoy, 15, died trying to save friend in
OL,4,Ctragic quarry accident
OL,6,FAn inquest held at Newport Coroner's
OL,7,Fcourt on Wednesday, 19 June, heard how
OL,8,Fthe incident was a "tragic accident"
OL,9,Fin which Myron reacted to save his
OL,10,Ffriend, who fell from a ledge of the
OL,11,Fquarry in the moments before he did.
OL,13,FCoroner Caroline Saunders said there
OL,14,Fwas no evidence of third-party
OL,15,Finvolvement despite rumours at the
OL,16,Ftime.
OL,18,FShe also concluded there was no
OL,19,Fevidence to suggest Myron intended to
OL,20,Fharm himself or end his own life.
