OL,6,FMs Saunders first read the evidence of
OL,7,Fwitness Lloyd Whitelock who saw the
OL,8,Fincident unfold from a distance in his
OL,9,Fback garden. Ms Saunders said the
OL,10,Fevidence needed to be taken with some
OL,11,Fcaution due to limited visibility,
OL,12,Fhowever the evidence was key in
OL,13,Fhelping police piece together what
OL,14,Fhappened.
