OL,3,CBoy, 15, died trying to save friend in
OL,4,Ctragic quarry accident
OL,6,FThe statement said: "At around 6.30pm
OL,7,Fsomething caught my vision... at first
OL,8,Fit appeared to be one person. The
OL,9,Fperson came from nowhere and walked
OL,10,Fclose to the edge. I continued to
OL,11,Fwatch. At this stage the person stood
OL,12,Fat the edge of the quarry and appeared
OL,13,Ftall. I later realised when (they)
OL,14,Ffell there were two people."
OL,16,FMr Whitelock said there was a "slight
OL,17,Fdelay" between the first and second
OL,18,Fperson falling.
