OL,4,Ctragic quarry accident
OL,6,FHe continued: "I was in total shock
OL,7,Fand called 999. Having processed it
OL,8,Fproperly there were two people and I'm
OL,9,Fsure they did not jump."
OL,11,FHe added how he had struggled to sleep
OL,12,Fsince witnessing the tragic incident.
OL,13,FMs Saunders next read a police
OL,14,Finterview with the teenage girl who
OL,15,Falso fell. She is not being named to
OL,16,Fprotect her identity.
