OL,3,CBoy, 15, died trying to save friend in
OL,4,Ctragic quarry accident
OL,6,FShe told officers at the time that she
OL,7,Fhad little recollection of what
OL,8,Fhappened, but had some flashbacks. She
OL,9,Fsaid neither she nor Myron went to the
OL,10,Fquarry with the intention of harming
OL,11,Fthemselves and that Myron seemed
OL,12,F"fine" in himself in the lead-up to
OL,13,Fthe incident. She added that the pair
OL,14,Fhad gone there after school as friends
OL,15,Fto admire the view.
