OL,3,CBoy, 15, died trying to save friend in
OL,4,Ctragic quarry accident
OL,6,FDetective chief inspector Leigh
OL,7,FHolborn was called as a witness during
OL,8,Fthe inquest. He stated he did not
OL,9,Fattend the incident, however had
OL,10,Foverall responsibility for the
OL,11,Fincident.
OL,13,FHe said investigations revealed how
OL,14,Fthe quarry was a spot frequented by
OL,15,Fyoung people who enjoyed the views. He
OL,16,Fsaid fencing has since been erected in
OL,17,Fthe area to restrict access.
