OL,6,FHe added that the teenage girl's fall
OL,7,Fwas broken by the quarry and branches,
OL,8,Fwhereas Myron's likely was not.
OL,10,FHe said having spoken to Myron's
OL,11,Ffamily, friends and school, he was a
OL,12,F"happy boy" and that "no mental health
OL,13,Fconcerns had been raised".
OL,15,FHe said there was evidence to suggest
OL,16,FMyron was looking forward to the
OL,17,Ffuture, and that he had charged his
OL,18,Flaptop ready for school the following
OL,19,Fday.
