OL,6,FHe added: "From the messages I have
OL,7,Fread (between Myron and his friend)
OL,8,Fthere was nothing there to suggest
OL,9,Fthere was a suicide pact."
OL,11,FMs Saunders concluded that Myron's
OL,12,Fdeath was caused by "a tragic
OL,13,Faccident". She confirmed his medical
OL,14,Fcause of death as multiple injuries
OL,15,Fcaused by a fall.
